title: Georges Seurat Final Study for “Bathers at Asnières” Tray
description:
Tray developed from Georges Seurat’s Final Study for "Bathers at Asnières", 1883, from the Art Institute of Chicago’s collection.

Give your decor an artistic lift with a custom porcelain tray featuring Georges Seurat’s work.  Can be used for display or function.

  • Dimensions: 4.25 x 5.25 x .5 in.
  • Box Dimensions: 4.75 x 6.75 x .75 in.
  • Material: Porcelain
  • Microwave and Dishwasher Safe
